{"type": "article", "id": 5663, "title": "Luna 橱柜", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-29T08:06:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233838xrwFEzmNpasUOXe8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t西班牙女性设计师 Patricia Urquiola 日前为法国家具品牌 Coedition 设计了一款橱柜，名为「Luna」，于本周亮相巴黎家居装饰博览会。上方圆形的储存空间被中间的隔档分开，上部呈开放式橱柜，下部则由旋转开合的门档封起来，可旋转 90 度的门档方便用户将杂物隐藏在内部，亦可以呈半开合状，做成陈列展示柜。底部两个相交的胡桃木平板构成稳定的十字支架。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233836lvt5uSeyMwrHz1iT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233837eLElsZgw0zAph9xr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233837SVM97LZ5toExWhJN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233837ajcAJe4GWnElC3D7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}